    "# Why some methods work and others don't — registration examples + failure analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "**Question:** with the same locked-prior + sz-pinned warmstart, why does **M3-ICP-locked** (sum r@20 = 2.729) crush **P3 RANSAC** (0.870) and beat **C5** (2.067) on most subjects, *and* why does ICP catastrophically fail on 2 of the 6 subjects?\n",
    "\n",
    "**Approach.** Show one winner subject (767018) and one loser subject (782149) in detail.  Per subject, compare three methods that all consume the same LP+sz-pin warmstart:\n",
    "\n",
    "* **M3-ICP-locked** — locked-scale rigid (R, t) ICP only.  Scales are frozen to the GT-validated pins.\n",
    "* **C5** — v1 ensemble = best of {P1 TLS, P4 spectral, P6 BCPD} via density-priority dispatch.  Each member re-fits the full 7-DOF affine.\n",
    "* **P3 RANSAC** — RANSAC over 4-tuples → fits anisotropic 7-DOF affine on each sample → score by inlier count → refit.  Re-fits all 7 DOF including sxy, sz."
   ]
