    "**Reading the ICP traces.**\n",
    "\n",
    "* **767018, 767022, 788406, 790322 (winners)** — `d_med` decreases monotonically across iters; `|Δt|` decays toward 0.  ICP is in its convergence basin and finds an aligned solution.\n",
